 analysis,
 and alerting processes.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Records retention and disposition of security audit logs.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Routing of audit findings to downstream response,
 problem management,
 and compliance monitoring processes.
\end_layout

