caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 shall be routed to 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:4.02"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 intake via a Safety and Security category work order.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Confirmed operational security events not matching IoC criteria shall be routed to 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:3.06"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Findings satisfying the Recurring Incident spawn trigger — five (5) or more same-category events within a rolling thirty (30) day window — shall prompt Problem record intake under 
