nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Records Custodian
\series default
:
 The IT Director,
 serving as the Information Operations Records Custodian under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:1.11"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
,
 shall ensure audit logs generated under this policy are classified to the applicable Nevada Local Government Records Retention Schedule record series and retained accordingly.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Legal Hold Suspension
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall immediately suspend all automated and manual log disposition actions upon notification of any active legal hold,
 public records preservation requirement,
 audit,
 or incident investigation,
 in accordance with 
\series bold
Policy 
