caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 (IT Asset Management Policy),
 retained audit logs generated by that system shall be preserved through the centralized log repository prior to media sanitization.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Custody Transfer
\series default
:
 The System and Network Administrator executing the decommissioning workflow shall verify that audit logs retained under Section 6.8 have been successfully transferred to the centralized log repository before initiating media sanitization under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:2.12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Verification
\series default
:
 The Assistant IT Director shall confirm successful log transfer and record the confirmation in the decommissioning work order prior to sanitization approval.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Legal Hold Exception
\series default
:
 Assets subject to an active legal hold,
 public records preservation requirement,
